            <div type="a">
                <column>5</column>
                <head>The Utter Annihilation of the Union</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>A transcript of a recent Breckinridge speech asserts that the Union is
                    forever dissolved.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>5</column>
                <head>Important Intelligence from the North</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Asserts that there is a considerable amount of commercial panic in the
                    North because Northerners fear that Europeans may begin a war with the United
                    States over the issue of the blockade of the South.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
